24/08/2009
NICOSIA, Cyprus -- Cypriots living all over the world gathered in Nicosia on Monday (August 24th) for the 16th Annual Conference of the Central Council of the World Federation for Overseas Cypriots (POMAK), the International Co-ordinating Committee Justice for Cyprus (PSEKA), and the Conference of the Executive Council of the World Organisation for Young Overseas Cypriots (NEPOMAK). The event, which ends Friday, will focus on efforts to reunify the divided island, the political situation, and media and communications issues. (Famagusta Gazette - 24/08/09; CNA - 23/08/09)
